48-a891-3630435e8721._CR0_98_460_460_SX48.jpg","background_color_end":"#ffffff","background_color_start":"#ffffff","border_color":"#211a28","border_radius":8,"border_style":"dashed","margin_bottom":15,"margin_left":0,"margin_right":0,"margin_top":5,"rating":5,"review_text":"This product went above and beyond what I expected. The build and performance are top-tier, and you can feel the quality right away. I’d absolutely recommend it to anyone considering it.","review_text_color":"#211a28","review_text_size":14,"reviewer_name":"Lauren J.","reviewer_name_size":16,"show_shadow":true,"star_color":"#211a28","star_size":16,"text_color":"#211a28","verified_icon_color":"#211a28"},"type":"customer_review"},"divider_yp8EHi":{"settings":{"alignment":"center","color":"#e4f9ff","margin_bottom":10,"margin_top":0,"max_width":"100%","style":"solid","thickness":1,"width":"100%"},"type":"divider"},"faq":{"settings":{"accordion_mode":true,"answer_1":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e✓ Free shipping on all orders\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e✓ 60-day money-back guarantee\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e✓ Free returns – keep it if you love it, return if you don’t\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e✓ No restocking fees, no questions asked\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","answer_10":"","answer_2":"\u003cp\u003eMost users notice a cleaner, healthier-feeling scalp right away. Fuller-looking, stronger hair typically appears within 4–8 weeks of regular use. Consistency is key.\u003c/p\u003e","answer_3":"\u003cp\u003eStimulates the scalp to activate healthier hair growth\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eRosemary extract boosts circulation around the follicles, encouraging stronger, fuller growth from the root.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eRebuilds weak, damaged strands with hydrolyzed keratin\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eKeratin peptides penetrate deeply to reinforce the hair shaft, reducing breakage and helping your hair grow longer without snapping.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/